      <title>奢侈品继承人声称其 130 亿美元爱马仕财富已消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/luxury-heir-alleges-his-13-billion-hermes-fortune-has-vanished</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱马仕 (Hermès) 奢侈品财富的一位八十多岁继承人因计划将财产留给园丁而引发去年的争议，但他可能也没什么可以赠予的了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/luxury-heir-alleges-his-13-billion-hermes-fortune-has-vanished</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国补贴成本不断膨胀 彰显绿色发展挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/germany-s-ballooning-subsidy-costs-show-challenge-of-going-green</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国正不堪重负地承担不断膨胀的可再生能源补贴，这让世界各国政府开始思考他们还能支撑绿色投资多久。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/germany-s-ballooning-subsidy-costs-show-challenge-of-going-green</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管德国经济意外下滑，欧元区经济增长仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区经济第二季度增长超过预期，主要国家的强劲扩张使该地区摆脱了德国意外经济萎缩的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因 GDP 增长意外上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区第二季度经济增长超出预期，缓解了人们对经济复苏步伐的担忧，欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
